# ANTHROPIC API KEY ARCHITECTURE:
# --------------------------------
# A SINGLE Anthropic API account can be used across ALL projects and social
# media accounts. The API key authenticates your organization, not individual
# projects. You can use the same ANTHROPIC_API_KEY for:
#   - Agent system on b0ase.com
#   - @b0ase Twitter automation
#   - @b0ase_com Twitter automation
#   - Any other b0ase related projects
#
# The differentiation happens in your APPLICATION CODE (not API keys):
#   - Different system prompts per agent
#   - Different task configurations per agent
#   - User_id scoping in database (RLS policies)
#   - Agent roles (developer, marketer, content, support)
#
# BILLING: All API usage from all projects goes to your Anthropic account.
# RATE LIMITS: Shared across all projects (monitor via Anthropic Console).
# ============================================================================

